                            "hoverhelp": "&lt;p>Set the administrative state of the configuration.&lt;/p>&lt;ul>&lt;li>To make active, set the check box.&lt;/li>&lt;li>To make inactive, clear the check box.&lt;/li>&lt;/ul>",
